Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.46,0:01:14.84,op jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隠してた感情が悲鳴を上げてる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.90,0:01:20.38,op jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確かな誓いを手に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.68,0:01:35.88,op jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇跡だけを求め
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.97,0:01:41.16,op jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消えない闇を彷徨う
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.21,0:01:51.72,op jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ここに居れば二度と未来見ること出来ない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.84,0:01:54.40,op jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今宵の月が誘って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.46,0:01:57.05,op jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,まだ言葉出せないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.10,0:02:00.88,op jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心の中叫び続けた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.95,0:02:07.30,op jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隠してた感情が悲鳴を上げてる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.36,0:02:12.46,op jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確かな誓いを手に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.50,0:02:18.02,op jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あとほんの少しだけ強くなれたなら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.08,0:02:24.74,op jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目の前にあるこの空越えて行くから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.92,0:02:33.45,op jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,この先にある未来に手を伸ばすから
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.46,0:01:14.84,op cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隱藏的感情發出了悲鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.90,0:01:20.38,op cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊握那確切的誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.68,0:01:35.88,op cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一味地尋求奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.97,0:01:41.16,op cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彷徨於無法磨滅的黑暗中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.21,0:01:51.72,op cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此停留將無法再次看到未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.84,0:01:54.40,op cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受今夜的月亮邀請
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.46,0:01:57.05,op cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然無法用言語表達
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.10,0:02:00.88,op cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在心中一直吶喊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.95,0:02:07.30,op cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隱藏的感情發出了悲鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.36,0:02:12.46,op cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊握那確切的誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.50,0:02:18.02,op cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如能再稍微變強
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.08,0:02:24.74,op cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便能跨越眼前的這片天空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.92,0:02:33.45,op cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向著未來伸出雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.70,0:22:22.77,ed jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高く高く　この手を伸ばして
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.83,0:22:33.26,ed jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「きっと　きっと」でもう一度願うから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.89,0:22:47.28,ed jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,とめどない想いは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.37,0:22:50.96,ed jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日常に呑まれて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.03,0:22:58.15,ed jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揺らめきながらまだ形を変えていて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.30,0:23:01.66,ed jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今更もう遅いかな
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.77,0:23:05.27,ed jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,返事もない自問自答
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.36,0:23:08.32,ed jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,すべてはそう　自分次第
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.38,0:23:13.01,ed jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終わりも始まりも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.08,0:23:19.95,ed jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高く高く　この手を伸ばして
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.01,0:23:27.04,ed jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優しい光を目指して羽ばたくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.10,0:23:34.40,ed jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心に灯した　情熱も抱いて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.48,0:23:43.31,ed jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「きっと　きっと」でもう一度願うから
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.70,0:22:22.77,ed cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將手伸往更高處
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.83,0:22:33.26,ed cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一次許願說「一定 一定」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.89,0:22:47.28,ed cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無盡的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.37,0:22:50.96,ed cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被日常所吞噬
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.03,0:22:58.15,ed cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在搖擺不定中再次發生了改變 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.30,0:23:01.66,ed cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今已經太晚了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.77,0:23:05.27,ed cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是沒有回答的自問自答
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.36,0:23:08.32,ed cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有都要看自己的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.38,0:23:13.01,ed cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終結也好開始也好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.08,0:23:19.95,ed cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將手伸往更高處
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.01,0:23:27.04,ed cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以溫柔的光芒為目標展翅高飛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.10,0:23:34.40,ed cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懷著在心中點燃的熱情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.48,0:23:43.31,ed cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一次許願說「一定 一定」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.11,0:00:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 來得真早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.69,0:00:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店子還是那麼不景氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.32,0:00:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少囉嗦 晚上可是很興隆的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.95,0:00:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 那張照片是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.41,0:00:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就有點說來話長了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.15,0:00:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.32,0:00:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遊戲？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.56,0:00:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AmuSphere 像是NERvGear的後繼機那樣的MMO
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.99,0:00:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼說 和SAO一樣是VRMMO嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.89,0:00:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Alfheim Online
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.13,0:00:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是發音為ALfheim
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.05,0:01:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是妖精國度的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.38,0:01:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖精…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.74,0:02:51.83,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖精們的國度
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.46,0:02:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖精國度… 休閒類嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.77,0:02:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 好像不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.95,0:03:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純技能制 重視玩家技能 推崇PK
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.56,0:03:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純技能制？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.23,0:03:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不存在所謂的等級
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.10,0:03:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各種技能靠反覆使用來提高
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.55,0:03:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥就依靠玩家的運動能力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.76,0:03:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難度真大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.62,0:03:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是沒有劍技而有魔法的SAO吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.74,0:03:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個現在非常有人氣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.78,0:03:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理由好像是因為能飛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.25,0:03:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能飛？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.65,0:03:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是妖精所以有翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.94,0:03:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是搭載了什麼飛行引擎 習慣了就能自由飛翔了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.71,0:03:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼控制啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.46,0:03:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道 但似乎相當難
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.46,0:03:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是 這可是要操縱人類所沒有的翅膀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.38,0:03:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要用背後的肌肉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.31,0:03:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 這高人氣遊戲和亞絲娜有什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.23,0:04:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.76,0:04:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟亞絲娜很像
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.68,0:04:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然會這麼想嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.45,0:04:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快告訴我 這是哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.55,0:04:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是遊戲裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.45,0:04:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ALfheim Online裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.83,0:04:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說是叫世界樹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.08,0:04:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這棵樹上面有個傳說的城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.71,0:04:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩家分成9個種族
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.74,0:04:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說是在比哪個種族最先到達城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.41,0:04:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛過去不就好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.47,0:04:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是有滯空時間 不能無限飛行的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.20,0:04:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有5名玩家按體格順序疊羅漢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.37,0:04:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以火箭式飛了上去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.45,0:04:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 雖然是笨個方法但不失為一個好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.41,0:04:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使那樣也夠不到世界樹最底下的樹枝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.40,0:04:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是拍到了幾張照片
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.75,0:04:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中一張拍到了奇異的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.04,0:05:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳥籠？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.54,0:05:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那個鳥籠的分辨率放到最大後
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.21,0:05:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就有了這個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.22,0:05:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 為什麼亞絲娜會在這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.16,0:05:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RCT progress
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.77,0:05:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以說明日奈的生命是我在維持著的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.77,0:05:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾基爾 這個軟件我可以拿走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.99,0:05:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 但是你打算去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.83,0:05:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要親眼確認一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.54,0:05:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了也無所謂的遊戲太弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.76,0:05:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還得去買驅動硬件呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.18,0:05:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用NERvGear也可以玩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.22,0:05:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為AmuSphere只是NERvGear的強化安全版而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.74,0:05:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.51,0:05:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把亞絲娜給救出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.91,0:05:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然 我們的戰鬥就無法結束
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.72,0:06:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 哪天來這裡搞個網聚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.12,0:06:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這個笨蛋 笨蛋 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.71,0:06:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.85,0:06:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.15,0:06:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.88,0:06:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還 還以為要死了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.15,0:06:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是冒失 慢點吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.72,0:06:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小直 關於昨晚的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.01,0:06:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.15,0:06:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.62,0:07:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧小直 我才能打起精神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.70,0:07:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會放棄的 一定會把亞絲娜救出來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.26,0:07:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 加油 我也想見見亞絲娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.94,0:07:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們一定能成為好朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.31,0:07:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 回頭見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.53,0:07:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儀式會在1周後的1月26日於這個病房裡舉行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.90,0:07:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也會叫上你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.35,0:07:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請再借一次力量給我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.47,0:08:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Link Start
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.02,0:08:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到ALfheim Online
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.39,0:08:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請先輸入性別和角色名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.00,0:08:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 你就是那個英雄桐人君啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.33,0:08:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 請決定你的種族
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.02,0:08:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請從9個種族中選擇一個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.80,0:08:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.11,0:08:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是影妖精族吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.47,0:08:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,角色的樣貌會隨機生成 可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.54,0:09:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 即將傳送您到影妖精族領地的根據地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.91,0:09:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你好運
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.96,0:09:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.90,0:09:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.35,0:09:56.63,tittle,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,500)\pos(641,450)}ALfheim·中立區域·古代森林
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.35,0:09:56.63,tittle,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,500)\pos(641,500)}2025年1月20日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.34,0:10:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.91,0:10:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明遇到了那種倒霉事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.95,0:10:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 這是哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.09,0:10:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.34,0:10:35.53,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法在一般區域裡即時登出 是否確定？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.34,0:10:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 數值…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.62,0:10:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事 BUG嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.95,0:10:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和SAO的數值一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.19,0:11:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事啊 這是在SAO裡面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.27,0:11:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.51,0:11:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.21,0:11:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.47,0:12:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我啊 結衣 認得出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.28,0:12:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又見面了呢 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.35,0:12:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結衣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.80,0:12:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.07,0:12:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓了吧 來吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.16,0:12:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.88,0:12:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.92,0:12:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.03,0:12:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.55,0:12:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇跡是存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.04,0:13:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 這究竟是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.63,0:13:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是說 這裡並不是SAO的世界啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.32,0:13:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一個叫做 「ALfheim Online」的遊戲裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.34,0:13:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.23,0:13:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界 我想是複製的Sword Art Online服務器資料製作而成的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.77,0:13:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,複製？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.02,0:13:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 主框架程序群 以及圖形建模都完全一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.81,0:13:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過主要系統的版本比較古老
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.04,0:13:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運營SAO的ARGUS在事後處理的時候被委託給了RECT
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.62,0:13:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 ARGUS的技術資產被RECT吸收利用了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.59,0:13:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 為什麼我的個人資料會出現在這裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.37,0:13:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看看爸爸的資料
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.02,0:14:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 這個就是在SAO裡爸爸使用過的人物資料本身
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.10,0:14:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存檔的格式也基本相同
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.37,0:14:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以兩個遊戲的共通的技能熟練度所以才會被繼承
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.52,0:14:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來二刀流不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.91,0:14:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而攜帶的道具 全部都損壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.90,0:14:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在被錯誤檢測程序發現之前最好還是丟棄掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.43,0:14:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.95,0:14:27.23,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要銷毀全部的道具嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.89,0:14:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這個技能熟練度怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.84,0:14:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熟練度的問題 只要GM不直接確認的話應該是沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.22,0:14:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.99,0:14:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來就不是封弊者 而是真正的作弊者了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.66,0:14:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那結衣你屬於哪類的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.46,0:15:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被分類為輔助玩家的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.16,0:15:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,模擬人格程序 導航妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.19,0:15:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是妖精的形態
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.50,0:15:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好癢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.28,0:15:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 你和以前一樣擁有管理者的權限嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.57,0:15:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 能做到的只有查詢和進入廣域地圖資料而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.58,0:15:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.56,0:15:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事實上 亞絲娜 你的媽媽好像在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.87,0:15:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.07,0:15:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這究竟是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.12,0:15:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞絲娜在SAO通關之後並沒有回到現實世界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.60,0:15:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得知在ALfheim裡有著和亞絲娜相似的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.98,0:16:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.19,0:16:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大致的地點我已經知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.22,0:16:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫做世界樹 應該就是那個了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.04,0:16:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽在那裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.12,0:16:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 我為什麼會在這個無人森林裡登陸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.47,0:16:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是應該被傳送到主城嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.10,0:16:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚 大概是位置情報損壞了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.76,0:16:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者是和附近的某個玩家搞混了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.21,0:16:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話還不如落在世界樹附近的位置呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.20,0:16:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是翅膀啊 要怎麼飛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.93,0:16:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有輔助控制桿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.53,0:16:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立起左手做出握東西的形狀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.54,0:16:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝里拉是上升
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.25,0:16:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向下推是下降
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.79,0:17:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左右搖是旋轉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.93,0:17:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按下按鈕是加速
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.15,0:17:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開按鈕則是減速
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.85,0:17:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翅膀發光的時候可以飛行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.00,0:17:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經過一段時間後 就必須讓翅膀休息
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.76,0:17:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 大體明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.37,0:17:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之最近的城市在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.92,0:17:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是西邊風之妖精的蘇伊露風標的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.50,0:17:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡是離這裡最近的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.66,0:17:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.87,0:17:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附近有玩家存在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.46,0:18:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉 莉法 等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.18,0:18:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊 蕾鵼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.99,0:18:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣逃到風妖精的領地的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.26,0:18:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾鵼 迴避
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.21,0:18:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 太纏人了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.53,0:18:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.84,0:18:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.13,0:18:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辦不到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.40,0:18:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西格魯特他們也一定已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.34,0:18:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會盡力吸引住他們的 至少也要擊落一個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.73,0:18:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.51,0:18:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾也要展現好的一面嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.09,0:19:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.26,0:19:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話 能贏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.03,0:19:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 不要停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.68,0:19:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.10,0:19:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾鵼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.09,0:19:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我們也是為了任務
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.85,0:20:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把錢和道具留下就放過你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.56,0:20:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝什麼紳士啊 影宗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.96,0:20:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久和女人做對手了 殺了她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.31,0:20:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我至少會拉一個人陪葬的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.70,0:20:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不怕死亡懲罰的就放馬過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.34,0:20:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺倔強的孩子嘛 那就沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.60,0:20:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,著陸很重要啊 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.07,0:20:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼呢 快點逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.10,0:21:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三名重戰士欺負一個女孩可不威風啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.16,0:21:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.70,0:21:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新手也敢大搖大擺地站出來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.53,0:21:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就如你所願的 幹掉你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.75,0:21:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 這些人可以砍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.78,0:21:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.44,0:21:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少他們應該是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.95,0:21:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.75,0:21:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.68,0:22:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個是誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
